    <h1 class="headline" itemprop="name">The Latest: Ebola in the United States</h1>

    
            <div class="dek" itemprop="description">
            A continually updated summary of all that&rsquo;s happened since the first patient was diagnosed on American soil.        </div>
    
    <div class="metadata">
